                                         "Transport Disembark",
                                         "Conquer Extras",
                                         "Enter Hut", "Frighten Hut",
                                         "Unit Move"

; Actor units will - under certain circumstances - be forced to try
; performing the following actions in the specified order after successfully
; performing "Attack".
